{"tid":1101420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打臉韓國瑜說法！國泰波音747昨抵高雄助維修","createTime":"2019-04-11T04:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T05:40:35.000Z","uid":41818,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a93246a587aceeef93b8e72b06bfa7feaf56e578","tid":1101420,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/toFFTBalyHDG3VunGujS1A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NDU2/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/9e0a0ec4fc291e7533522f2627d30ece\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtoFFTBalyHDG3VunGujS1A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NDU2%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F9e0a0ec4fc291e7533522f2627d30ece&h=8b5ee008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左為波音747貨機。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜自空降高雄參選以來，屢次的發言讓外界質疑對高雄根本完全不瞭解，日前其「F1賽車」政見跳票，他聲稱高雄國際機場（小港機場）無法讓波音747大型飛機起降，因此無法將賽車運至高雄。另外韓國瑜上月也向外媒提到，從雲嘉南地區一直到屏東，台灣南部目前沒有一個可以停靠波音747的大型機場，希望能趕快興建。上述兩項發言均被資深航空迷打臉，今（10）韓國瑜出訪美國之際，並非定期航班的國泰航空波音747-867(F)貨機降落高雄國際機場，再度引發網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空旗下的國泰港龍航空KA451班機，8日上午八時許自高國際機場起飛，原訂目的地為香港，卻突然返航迫降小港機場。民航局當時回應，飛機將執行內視鏡檢查，進一步瞭解發動機受損情況。另外，由於該架為香港籍的飛機，我方也會將調查內容通知香港民航局，在完成一連串手續，並確定修復後才會放飛。<br />\n<br />\n昨日國泰航空的貨機降落高雄，就有航迷判斷，應是國泰集團的「老大哥」載著維修的引擎來給「小老弟」，盼能盡快修復並且返回香港大本營，繼續投入飛行工作。<br />\n<br />\n而韓國瑜日前出訪澳門時，曾說道「高雄與澳門沒有直航班機」，不過事實上，有包含長榮航空、澳門航空與台灣虎航在營運高雄澳門直飛航線，每周總班次更多達32班，看來韓國瑜對於高雄以及飛機與航線的瞭解，似乎需要更用心做功課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%89%93%E8%87%89%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95-%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3747%E4%BB%8A%E6%8A%B5%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84-054014141.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%2589%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E9%259F%25B3747%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258A%25B5%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%259B%2584-054014141.html&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=989ee9e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%89%93%E8%87%89%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95-%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3747%E4%BB%8A%E6%8A%B5%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84-054014141.html</a>"},{"pid":"f3def4afa2da5445873e8b49ada08edf535cb061","tid":1101420,"uid":50658,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"on9廢老先信泡菜瑜<br />\n不過垃圾不分藍綠"},{"pid":"10620b57578e2b3e55458bc004224e12e34f49b5","tid":1101420,"uid":95,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"條友係咪戇鳩，基本fact check 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86b10302fc14fab0089bda5c0d2e0abf5082990","tid":1101420,"uid":52943,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"真係弱智選民出弱智政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a089a76de5f6ed1bf1449d9a6b4550fcaf805e5","tid":1101420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80dba9d47bd0a6950d6ccda7d04cbe6de235648","tid":1101420,"uid":39777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b86b10302fc14fab0089bda5c0d2e0abf5082990","tid":1101420,"uid":52943,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"真係弱智選民出弱智政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"互為因果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ac687e24b80cd56ddab8bed5547b16e9c3fa27","tid":1101420,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":